&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whop operates in fast-moving digital verticals. Risk is not a back-office function - it’s embedded in growth. As our first dedicated Payments Risk Specialist, you aren’t joining a legacy machine, you will help shape it.&amp;nbsp;We’re looking for a Payments Risk Specialist who can monitor, research and continuously improve transaction and merchant risk frameworks while enabling expansion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor transaction activity and merchant behavior across card and alternative payment rails&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze fraud patterns, chargeback trends, and abuse vectors, applying creative investigative skills to uncover the hidden trails of bad actors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Compliance on KYC, KYB, and onboarding risk controls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fine tune rules and thresholds to balance approval rates with loss mitigation. You understand that a blanket &quot;no&quot; is the easy way out but you aim for precision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design dashboards and alerts that surface emerging risk trends, building data narratives from the ground up&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work cross-functionally to prevent systemic exposure while preserving growth velocity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2–5 years in payments risk, fraud operations, or transaction monitoring with a strong analytical mindset with ability to interpret behavioral and financial signals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You thrive in greenfield environments. You possess the ability to make principled risk decisions under ambiguity and partial information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical mindset with ability to interpret behavioral and financial signals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a relentless &quot;can-do&quot; attitude. You don&#39;t wait for perfect engineering solutions; you build workarounds, push boundaries, and find a way&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You keep a sharp eye on UX. You understand that managing risk is about maximizing legitimate revenue, not just minimizing loss&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to make principled risk decisions under ambiguity and partial information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with digital goods, marketplaces, or creator platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposure to sponsor bank environments or card network monitoring programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your first 90 days will look like the following:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Within 30 days, you will deeply master Whop’s payment risk flows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Within 60 days, You take full ownership of the daily operation. You are applying your creative review skills to hunt down bad actors and making principled risk decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Within 90 days, you are detecting fraud patterns and escalating trends to our engineering teams to update fraud solutions within our product&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The expected salary range for this position is $100,000 to $130,000 annually, with final compensation determined based on experience, skills, and qualifications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;✅ Competitive equity package&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;❤️ Unlimited PTO, with full health, vision, dental coverage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🍕 Lunch &amp;amp; dinner paid for Monday through Friday&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🏋️‍♀️ Free Equinox membership&lt;/li&gt;
