&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience (3+ years) building and managing partnerships in payments, fintech, or financial servicesStrong ability to operate under pressure and drive resolution across complex, real-time operational challenges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High ownership with a clear sense of urgency and strong prioritization across multiple workstreams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data-driven mindset with the ability to translate numbers into clear business impact and actionable insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills with the ability to simplify complexity and align both internal and external stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable engaging with senior stakeholders and executives, internally and externally&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with global partners across multiple regions is a strong advantage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with multi-PSP environments, payment methods, or BNPL ecosystems is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
